InteractionText: I don't want to take a bath! I love the warm smell of garbage. Noooo! Don't blast me with water from a pressure washer!
ReplyTexts: ['(Walk off while covering its nose)', 'A good trash can takes a bath without complaints.']

InteractionText: Bubble tea, banana peal, apple core, half of a burger... Not interested? Just leave them to me! Bow to the greedy gobbler of the leftovers!
Gobbling up the trash and upholding my guard dutiesâ€”one day... one of these days, I will ascend to Babylonia and become a Babylonia trash can! Don't be shy! Quick, chuck everything into my mouth!
Gray! Nail! The trash can of all trash cans, the ruler of garbage, the king! The Lord! The ultimate trash can of all time!
Oof, my legs are so numb from sitting in the same position. I just want to hop off this pedestal and go wander around the garden with everyone!
Do you see the parfait and the cake on that table right there? They make me so hungry! I am craving dessert. That dessert must be for me, right?
ReplyTexts: ['Walk over to the table and sit down to eat.']

InteractionText: Achoo! These flowers are beautiful! And they smell so good. Try it! Achoo! Why am I sneezing? Let's try again. Achoo! Come, come and smell it with me.
ReplyTexts: ["You're probably allergic to pollen.", 'Let me smell it, too. Achoo!']

InteractionText: Commandant, it's time to go to bed. You're gaming again? It'll ruin your skin! This is my final warning. If you don't go to bed now...
ReplyTexts: ['Put down your phone and interrupt the spell.', 'Start twisting on your own.']

InteractionText: I wish I could go fishing by the pond. I don't wanna stand guard anymore, I just wanna go fishing!
ReplyTexts: ['I caught a big fish that weighs over 3 pounds today!', 'I am not in the air force.']

InteractionText: Delicious Basque cheesecake and chocolate parfait! Take a bite, take a bite! (The parfait that never melts and the cake that never spoils smell so sweet and tempting, but no one knows how long they've been sitting here!)
ReplyTexts: ['Take a bite!', 'Resist temptation and walk away with your eyes shut.']
